#!/bin/sh
# Advisory reminder to keep reference docs in sync with code changes.
# Does not block the push.

cat <<'EOF'

Reference-file checklist before pushing:
  [ ] ROADMAP.md    — status changes, new items added or completed
  [ ] CHANGELOG.md  — notable changes in this push under [Unreleased]
  [ ] README.md     — user-facing features or setup changes
  [ ] FUNCTIONS.md  — new calculator functions, modules, or utilities
  [ ] tone.md       — voice or style rule changes (rarely, but flag if so)

If everything is covered, carry on. Push proceeding.

EOF

exit 0
